---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "The Projects"
description: "Uncost's project briefs — public review drafts. No budget, build, pilot, or launch is approved."
---
{% from "partials/content-needed.njk" import block as gap %}
<section class="blk blk--first">
  <p class="eyebrow">The Projects</p>
  <h1 class="sec">The projects.</h1>
  <p class="lead">Public review drafts. No budget, build, pilot, or launch is approved; every brief is a reviewed dossier, not a shipped product.</p>
  {{ gap("projects-index-intro", "the export's 'one system, three parts' hub framing and per-project blurbs are design-authored; author from dossiers once approved") }}
</section>
<section class="blk blk--cream2">
  <div class="doc-list">
{%- for project in catalog.projects %}
    <a class="doc-row" href="/projects/{{ project.slug }}/"><span class="doc-id">{{ project.id }}</span><span class="doc-title">{{ project.display }}</span><span class="status status--planned">Draft</span></a>
{%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
<section class="blk">
  <p class="eyebrow">Longer horizon</p>
  <div class="prose prose--flush">
  {{ catalog.longerHorizon | mdSection | safe }}
  </div>
</section>
